  documentBody: There are documented instances of Ashley taking full credit for work
    that was my own individual effort. In her raise request letter, she listed accomplishments
    and projects that I created and executed, framing it as though it was her sole
    accomplishment. This is not merely failing to provide acknowledgment - it is
    overtly claiming ownership over work that 95% of the creative ideation and labour
    fell onto my shoulders.
